1
00:00:03,125 --> 00:00:05,125
- Wanna kill yourself with me?

2
00:00:16,291 --> 00:00:18,083
Come on.
I didn't mean it,

3
00:00:18,166 --> 00:00:21,125
but honestly...

4
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:27,125
<i>[COALAMODE.'S</i>
<i>"Nanairo Symphony"]</i>

5
00:00:27,208 --> 00:00:29,833
♪♪

6
00:00:29,916 --> 00:00:32,875
<i>[singing in Japanese]</i>

7
00:00:32,958 --> 00:00:41,875
♪♪

8
00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:50,916
♪♪

9
00:00:51,000 --> 00:00:59,916
♪♪

10
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:08,916
♪♪

11
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:18,000
♪♪

12
00:01:18,083 --> 00:01:27,041
